A service/adapter may deal with multiple environments, especially on the provider side. This class simply represents a list of environments. This class is not a singleton, rather a POJO for environment lists. In an actual implementation it is suggested to provide this list as a singleton as it is not a 'dynamic' structure, rather fairly static.
